init_text:
A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She’s unaware that she’s actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who’s fallen for her, and is certain he’s going to get it right this time.

One day,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She’s on her bed, and she is very tense.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She has had one bad date after another.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It seems like she just can’t find the guy of her dreams.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: After all, she was meeting this new guy in a park.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It was a beautiful day, and she was looking forward to it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Then, she heard a strange noise.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It seemed like a voice, but she couldn't make out any words.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It was the voice of a man.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I am your true love," said the voice.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Suddenly, the music comes back on.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She looked around, trying to find where the voice was coming from, but there was no one there.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She couldn't move on until she dealt with her true love first.
